Change a
{jjdhr_heat_p}
status between
{jjdhe_racing}
and
{jjdhe_stabled},
or rename its
{jjdhm_silks}.

{jjds_arguments}

// ⟦axd_optional axd_defaulted⟧
* {jjda_file}

// ⟦axd_required⟧
* {jjdt_firemark}
(positional) — target
{jjdhr_heat}

// ⟦axd_optional⟧
* `--racing` — set status to
{jjdhe_racing}

// ⟦axd_optional⟧
* `--stabled` — set status to
{jjdhe_stabled}

// ⟦axd_optional⟧
* {jjda_silks}
— new display name

*Requirements:* At least one of `--racing`, `--stabled`, or {jjda_silks} must be provided.

{jjds_stdout} None

{jjds_exit_uniform} 0 success, non-zero error.

{jjds_behavior}

. Read
{jjdgr_gallops}
from file
. Verify
{jjdhr_heat}
exists with given
{jjdt_firemark}
. Verify at least one argument provided (`--racing`, `--stabled`, or {jjda_silks})
. If status change requested:
.. Error if heat is
{jjdhe_retired}
(terminal state)
.. Error if `--racing` and heat already
{jjdhe_racing}
.. Error if `--stabled` and heat already
{jjdhe_stabled}
.. Update
{jjdhm_status}
to new value
. If {jjda_silks} provided:
.. Update
{jjdhm_silks}
to new value
. Write transformed
{jjdgr_gallops}
to file (atomic)

